#!backend/*.csproj
#!*.sln

**/CLAUDE.md
**/docs/
frontend/docs/
backend/docs/
**/[fF]eatures/**/context.md

# Deployment files that must be tracked (override the broad *.yml and Scripts/ rules above).
!/scripts/
!/scripts/**/*.sh
!/scripts/**/*.sql
!docker-compose.yml
!docker-compose.*.yml
!.github/workflows/*.yml
docker-compose.override.yml

**/seed/**